   "source": [
    "\n",
    "The raw attribution values include both positive and negative contributions.  \n",
    "For ranking and visualization, the absolute attribution values were used and normalized between `0` and `1`.\n",
    "\n",
    "The normalized scores range from `0.0000` to `1.0000`, and almost all edges receive a non-zero attribution score.  \n",
    "The convergence delta is approximately `0.0012`, indicating that the Integrated Gradients approximation is stable for this explanation.\n",
    "\n",
    "These normalized edge scores will be used to rank and visualize the most influential edges for the fraud prediction."
   ]
