    "- the normalized absolute attribution score, used for ranking;\n",
    "- the raw Integrated Gradients attribution, which preserves the sign of the contribution.\n",
    "\n",
    "A positive raw attribution means that the edge contributes positively to the target fraud probability, while a negative attribution means that the edge pushes against the fraud prediction."
