    "### 10.1 Top Nodes and Derived Edges\n",
    "\n",
    "To inspect the explanation, the nodes are ranked according to their learned causal importance score.  \n",
    "Since this explainer does not directly learn an edge mask, edge scores are derived by averaging the scores of the source and target nodes connected by each edge.\n",
    "\n",
    "These derived edge scores are used only for ranking and visualization, while the primary explanation remains node-based."
   ]
