    "### 10.2 Visualization\n",
    "\n",
    "The following plot visualizes the top-ranked derived edges obtained from the CausGNN-style node mask.\n",
    "\n",
    "The primary explanation learned by this method is node-based.  \n",
    "Edge scores are therefore derived by averaging the importance scores of the source and target nodes of each edge.\n",
    "\n",
    "The target fraud node is highlighted in red, while the other nodes are colored according to their labels.  \n",
    "Edge thickness is proportional to the derived edge score."
